<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
<p>Welcome to socshelf.com. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your information when you visit our website.</p>

<h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect various types of personal information from our users, including but not limited to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Identifiers such as name, email address, and IP address.</li>
    <li>Commercial information such as transaction history.</li>
    <li>Internet activity such as browsing history and interaction with our website.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>
<p>The information we collect is used for the following purposes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>To provide and improve our services.</li>
    <li>To personalize user experience.</li>
    <li>To comply with legal requirements.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
<p>We may share your personal information with:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Service providers who assist us in operating our website.</li>
    <li>Third-party partners for marketing purposes.</li>
    <li>Government authorities when required by law.</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
<p>Under the CCPA, you have the right to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Request access to your personal information.</li>
    <li>Request deletion of your personal information.</li>
    <li>Not be discriminated against for exercising your privacy rights.</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. How to Exercise Your Rights</h2>
<p>To exercise your privacy rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@socshelf.com">privacy@socshelf.com</a>. We will verify your identity before processing your request.</p>

<h2>7. Security of Your Information</h2>
<p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure.</p>

<h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The effective date of the current version is [Effective Date]. We will notify you of any changes by posting the updated policy on our website.</p>

<h2>9. Contact Information</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@socshelf.com">privacy@socshelf.com</a>.</p>
